rows.label: qst200808_msg0001
rows.name: What's the matter? You need anything?

rows.label: qst200808_msg0002
rows.name:
We're looking for a tree brace...
Do you have one we could use?

rows.label: qst200808_msg0003
rows.name:
A tree brace?
Why on Alst would you need one?

rows.label: qst200808_msg0006
rows.name:
Well, for a Saffronia tree, you'll need
an exceedingly sturdy one for sure.

rows.label: qst200808_msg0009
rows.name:
But a brace for a big tree like that'd
need some special ingredients and
processing.

rows.label: qst200808_msg0011
rows.name:
I should be able to make do with
five pieces of Healing Teak, found
all across Gula.

rows.label: qst200808_msg0012
rows.name:
Thank you!
We'll get on that straight away!

rows.label: qst200808_msg0015
rows.name:
Hotaru over there.
Stare at processing process.
